This directory contains files needed to build the simple_felix prototype
driver.  Simple_felix connects CISM to the Albany/FELIX external dynamic core.
Building simple_felix requires access to the Albany/FELIX installation.
For more information on Albany/FELIX, please send an email to
ikalash@sandia.gov or agsalin@sandia.gov.

